#: resources/animate.glade:78
msgid "Animated"
msgstr "Animado"

#: resources/animate.glade:85
msgid ""
"Hue shows the peak magnitude s(n); brightness follows the traveling wave |"
"cos(arg z + φ)|, floored so nulls stay visible.\n"
"\n"
"Animated: bright regions sweep along the structure as the phase advances."
msgstr ""
"El tono muestra la magnitud pico s(n); el brillo sigue la onda viajera |"
"cos(arg z + φ)|, con un piso para que los nulos permanezcan visibles.\n"
"\n"
"Animado: las regiones brillantes recorren la estructura a medida que avanza "
"la fase."

#: resources/animate.glade:86
msgid "Instantaneous"
msgstr "Instantáneo"

#: resources/animate.glade:96
msgid ""
"Diverging hue shows the instantaneous sign of the displayed quantity: cold "
"negative, hot positive; brightness carries the magnitude s(n).\n"
"\n"
"Animated: regions swap poles as the phase advances."
msgstr ""
"El tono divergente muestra el signo instantáneo de la magnitud mostrada: "
"frío negativo, cálido positivo; el brillo transmite la magnitud s(n).\n"
"\n"
"Animado: las regiones intercambian polos a medida que avanza la fase."

#: resources/animate.glade:97
msgid "Polarity"
msgstr "Polaridad"

#: resources/animate.glade:107
msgid ""
"Cyclic hue wheel shows the phase angle arg z + φ; brightness carries the "
"magnitude s(n).\n"
"\n"
"Animated: the whole wheel rotates as the phase advances."
msgstr ""
"La rueda de tono cíclica muestra el ángulo de fase arg z + φ; el brillo "
"transmite la magnitud s(n).\n"
"\n"
"Animado: toda la rueda gira a medida que avanza la fase."

#: resources/animate.glade:108
msgid "Phase Hue"
msgstr "Tono de fase"

#: resources/animate.glade:118
msgid ""
"Diverging hue shows the instantaneous charge sign; brightness carries the "
"current envelope s(|I|).\n"
"\n"
"Animated: one view of charge and current a quarter cycle apart."
msgstr ""
"El tono divergente muestra el signo instantáneo de la carga; el brillo "
"transmite la envolvente de corriente s(|I|).\n"
"\n"
"Animado: una sola vista de carga y corriente separadas un cuarto de ciclo."

#: resources/animate.glade:119
msgid "Current + Charge"
msgstr "Corriente + Carga"

#: resources/animate.glade:136
msgid "Static"
msgstr "Estático"

#: resources/animate.glade:143
msgid ""
"Rainbow ramp of this frequency step's peak magnitude s(n) at full "
"brightness.\n"
"\n"
"Static: the phase-invariant baseline; colors hold still during playback."
msgstr ""
"Rampa de arcoíris de la magnitud pico s(n) de este paso de frecuencia a "
"brillo total.\n"
"\n"
"Estático: la línea base invariante con la fase; los colores permanecen fijos "
"durante la reproducción."

#: resources/animate.glade:144
msgid "Amplitude"
msgstr "Amplitud"

#: resources/animate.glade:154
msgid ""
"Hue ramps the per-region standing-wave ratio: cold traveling, hot standing; "
"brightness carries the magnitude s(n).\n"
"\n"
"Static: a phase-invariant read; colors hold still during playback."
msgstr ""
"El tono representa la relación de onda estacionaria por región: frío "
"viajera, cálido estacionaria; el brillo transmite la magnitud s(n).\n"
"\n"
"Estático: una lectura invariante con la fase; los colores permanecen fijos "
"durante la reproducción."

#: resources/animate.glade:155
msgid "Standing/Traveling"
msgstr "Estacionaria/Viajera"

#: resources/animate.glade:165
msgid ""
"Hue ramps each segment's contribution to the selected far-field direction; "
"brightness carries the magnitude s(n).\n"
"\n"
"Static: a phase-invariant read; colors hold still during playback."
msgstr ""
"El tono representa la contribución de cada segmento a la dirección de campo "
"lejano seleccionada; el brillo transmite la magnitud s(n).\n"
"\n"
"Estático: una lectura invariante con la fase; los colores permanecen fijos "
"durante la reproducción."

#: resources/animate.glade:166
msgid "Far-field Contribution"
msgstr "Contribución de campo lejano"

#: resources/animate.glade:180
msgid ""
"Power-law transfer n^γ of the normalized magnitude.\n"
"\n"
"γ = 1 is linear amplitude; γ = 0.5 expands weak regions; γ = 2 shows the "
"squared magnitude — |I|² is proportional to per-segment dissipated power "
"(and its radiated-power contribution via radiation resistance), |q|² to "
"stored electrostatic energy."
msgstr ""
"Transferencia de ley de potencia n^γ de la magnitud normalizada.\n"
"\n"
"γ = 1 es amplitud lineal; γ = 0.5 expande las regiones débiles; γ = 2 "
"muestra la magnitud al cuadrado — |I|² es proporcional a la potencia "
"disipada por segmento (y su contribución a la potencia radiada mediante la "
"resistencia de radiación), |q|² a la energía electrostática almacenada."

#: resources/animate.glade:181
msgid "Power"
msgstr "Potencia"

#: resources/animate.glade:191
msgid ""
"Logarithmic transfer over a user range R, the RF-standard 20·log₁₀ amplitude "
"decibels.\n"
"\n"
"R sets the visible dynamic range; detail below the floor 10^(−R/20) clips to "
"the bottom color."
msgstr ""
"Transferencia logarítmica sobre un rango R definido por el usuario, los "
"decibelios de amplitud estándar de RF 20·log₁₀.\n"
"\n"
"R fija el rango dinámico visible; el detalle por debajo del piso 10^(−R/20) "
"se recorta al color inferior."

#: resources/animate.glade:192 resources/xnec2c.glade:11670
#: resources/xnec2c.glade:13045
msgid "dB"
msgstr "dB"

#: resources/animate.glade:202
msgid ""
"Inverse hyperbolic sine: linear below the knee k, logarithmic above.\n"
"\n"
"Keeps near-null currents visible while compressing strong peaks, like a lin-"
"log instrument scale."
msgstr ""
"Seno hiperbólico inverso: lineal por debajo de la rodilla k, logarítmico por "
"encima.\n"
"\n"
"Mantiene visibles las corrientes cercanas a nulo mientras comprime los picos "
"fuertes, como una escala de instrumento lin-log."

#: resources/animate.glade:203
msgid "Asinh"
msgstr "Asinh"

#: resources/animate.glade:213
msgid ""
"μ-law companding, the telephony-standard bounded log curve.\n"
"\n"
"Lifts weak detail without a hard floor; 48.16 dB compression is the classic "
"μ = 255."
msgstr ""
"Compansión ley μ, la curva logarítmica acotada estándar de telefonía.\n"
"\n"
"Realza el detalle débil sin un piso abrupto; la compresión de 48.16 dB es la "
"μ = 255 clásica."

#: resources/animate.glade:214
msgid "μ-law"
msgstr "Ley μ"

#: resources/animate.glade:224
msgid ""
"Reinhard rational compressor (1+k)·n/(n+k), the photographic HDR tone-map.\n"
"\n"
"Preserves midtones while rolling highlights off smoothly; k sets the knee."
msgstr ""
"Compresor racional de Reinhard (1+k)·n/(n+k), el mapeo tonal HDR "
"fotográfico.\n"
"\n"
"Preserva los tonos medios mientras atenúa suavemente las altas luces; k fija "
"la rodilla."

#: resources/animate.glade:225
msgid "Reinhard"
msgstr "Reinhard"

#: resources/animate.glade:235
msgid ""
"Hyperbolic tangent soft limiter tanh(a·n)/tanh(a).\n"
"\n"
"Raises midrange contrast and saturates gently toward the peak, like "
"amplifier compression; a sets the steepness."
msgstr ""
"Limitador suave de tangente hiperbólica tanh(a·n)/tanh(a).\n"
"\n"
"Aumenta el contraste en el rango medio y satura suavemente hacia el pico, "
"como la compresión de un amplificador; a fija la pendiente."

#: resources/animate.glade:236
msgid "Sigmoid"
msgstr "Sigmoide"

#: resources/animate.glade:246
msgid ""
"Identity: every magnitude renders at full brightness.\n"
"\n"
"The color projection alone carries the information."
msgstr ""
"Identidad: toda magnitud se renderiza a brillo total.\n"
"\n"
"Solo la proyección de color transmite la información."

#: resources/animate.glade:247 resources/settings/cairo_settings.glade:56
msgid "None"
msgstr "Ninguno"

#: resources/animate.glade:259 src/rdpattern_ui.c:329 src/rdpattern_ui.c:337
#: src/rdpattern_ui.c:344
msgid "Near Field Animation"
msgstr "Animación de campo cercano"

#: resources/animate.glade:351
msgid ""
"Scrub the animation phase manually.\n"
"\n"
"Disabled while the animation is running."
msgstr ""
"Ajustar manualmente la fase de animación.\n"
"\n"
"Deshabilitado mientras la animación está en curso."

#: resources/animate.glade:368
msgid "φ 0°"
msgstr "φ 0°"

#: resources/animate.glade:382
msgid "Phase"
msgstr "Fase"

#: resources/animate.glade:405
